title: Wal-Mart, others speed up deliveries to shoppers - KXAN-TV Austin
text:
In this Feb. 13, 2015 file photo, a worker places an item in a box for shipment during a media tour of the new Amazon.com fulfillment center in DuPont, Wash. The center is one of 50 around the country and three in the Puget Sound area that process and ship Amazon customer orders using a mix of robotic technology and human employees.
 KXAN-TV Austin.
